steps to create a simple project

 - click on "new item"
 
 - select "freestyle project"
 
 - go to "build steps" and select "Execute shell"
 
 - in the text box write commands 
   echo "Hello from Challenge 1"
   
 - click on save and then on build now
 
 - in build history you can see the first build completed

 - click on it and select "Console Output"
